    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let’s get started!</strong></p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>beef mince </strong>to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until starting to brown, breaking it up with a wooden spoon as you go</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
