        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>fresh tagliatelle</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>tagliatelle</strong> for 3-4 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>tagliatelle</strong>, reserving 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml] </span>of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
