    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tomato paste</strong>,<strong> beef stock mix</strong>,<strong> soy sauce </strong>and 75ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[115ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml] </span>of the <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until thickened and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>bolognese ragù</strong></p>",
